et posteris meis stirpiqu.

33:46.816 --> 33:47.859
Susie...

33:48.943 --> 33:49.861
did you see that?

34:05.835 --> 34:07.211
My name is Susie Putnam.

34:09.380 --> 34:11.674
Blood of Dorothea Putnam,

34:11.758 --> 34:14.260
who gave you passage across
the ocean when no one else would,

34:14.343 --> 34:17.638
who cut you down from the hanging tree
when no one else would.

34:18.222 --> 34:19.849
The Walkers are my friends.

34:22.602 --> 34:23.895
Please don't hurt them.

34:35.198 --> 34:38.242
It's working, isn't it

34:38.326 --> 34:41.245
Yes, as long as we four
remain focused, it just might.

34:46.042 --> 34:48.211
Faustus, you brought me here?

34:48.294 --> 34:50.838
-I did, Sister Zelda--
-I have to go back. My family needs me.

34:50.922 --> 34:52.924
Your sworn duty is here, Zelda!

34:53.007 --> 34:54.884
Lady Blackwood has gone into labor.

34:58.596 --> 34:59.847
Damn you, Faustus.

35:00.640 --> 35:03.351
I'll need clean towels, fresh water,
and Prudence.

35:03.434 --> 35:06.312
-Prudence?
-Yes, I'll need help,

35:06.395 --> 35:08.189
and this is no place for a man.

35:08.648 --> 35:10.733
And that very much includes you.

35:15.029 --> 35:15.863
Yes.

35:17.365 --> 35:18.825
You'll be just fine.

35:21.911 --> 35:23.621
Where did Aunt Zelda go

35:23.704 --> 35:25.873
Can the protection spell hold
with just three of us?

35:25.957 --> 35:30.128
It's a bit dodgy, but if three of us just
pick up the slack and no one else disap--

35:30.628 --> 35:31.546
No!

35:33.548 --> 35:34.841
Luke, what am I doing here?

35:34.924 --> 35:37.218
I teleported you here.
It's no use trying to leave.

35:37.301 --> 35:39.303
I've bound you to the Academy,
and you have to stay.

35:39.387 --> 35:42.014
Why -Because you belong here with us now,

35:42.098 --> 35:44.142
with your own kind,
safe inside these walls,

35:44.225 --> 35:46.269
standing with the coven
with your warlock brothers.

35:46.352 --> 35:47.228
With me, Ambrose.

35:47.311 --> 35:50.565
-No. You don't understand. I have to--
-No, you don't understand!

35:50.648 --> 35:53.025
I couldn't leave you out there
to die, Ambrose.

35:53.526 --> 35:54.986
Because I love you.

36:04.412 --> 36:06.914
The witches are getting stronger
out there, I can sense it.

36:06.998 --> 36:09.458
Ms. Wardwell,
it's just me and Aunt Hilda now.

36:09.834 --> 36:12.253
I'm fading, love.
I don't think I can hold out much longer.

36:12.336 --> 36:15.548
Sabrina, if youÂ and your Aunt
can't maintain the spell,

36:15.631 --> 36:18.301
the Thirteen will throw open
every door and window.

36:18.384 --> 36:21.554
The mortals will be unprotected
when the Red Angel arrives,

36:21.637 --> 36:23.514
and there will be no escaping his sword.

36:23.598 --> 36:24.765
Pitch in at any time.

36:24.849 --> 36:27.810
I fear we would still falter
before the witching hour ends.

36:27.894 --> 36:32.148
Then there's the matter of Mr. Kinkle,
Miss Putnam, Miss Walker.

36:32.231 --> 36:35.943
They're out there,
facing their own personal assaults.

36:36.027 --> 36:38.654
No, the time for defense is over.

36:39.030 --> 36:40.907
It's time to go on the offensive.

36:40.990 --> 36:42.533
How would we even do that?

36:42.617 --> 36:46.078
As a matter of fact, I have an idea,
but it would mean your Aunt Hilda here

36:46.162 --> 36:47.914
holding down the fort alone for a bit.

36:47.997 --> 36:50.583
-Alone? Bloody hell!
-Sabrina, we are running out of time.

36:50.666 --> 36:54.962
Fine, let's do it. Aunt Hilda, hold on.
Salem, stay here and watch Aunt Hilda.

36:56.047 --> 36:58.633
Just do it, Salem!
I'll be back as soon as I can.

37:04.555 --> 37:07.308
In the end,
there was only one way to accomplish

37:07.391 --> 37:09.727
what the Dark Lord wanted.

37:10.561 --> 37:13.397
Make it so that Sabrina would have
no other option.

37:14.941 --> 37:19.028
There would only be one path
to save the mortals.

37:22.198 --> 37:24.450
The Path of Night.

37:25.993 --> 37:28.871
And so we went
back to the clearing in the woods,

37:29.705 --> 37:34.252
where this story first began
16 years ago.

37:34.543 --> 37:35.753
Wait...

37:35.836 --> 37:38.547
Ms. Wardwell,
this is where my Dark Baptism...

37:38.631 --> 37:40.800
...almost but not quite took place.

37:43.678 --> 37:44.720
Ms. Wardwell...

37:45.429 --> 37:47.723
what is the Book of the Beast doing here?

37:49.558 --> 37:50.685
The kind of...

37:51.560 --> 37:54.188
power you'll need
to save Greendale will...

37:54.939 --> 37:56.023
require you to--

37:56.107 --> 37:57.525
Sign my name?

37:58.776 --> 38:01.570
Exchange my freedom for power?

38:03.447 --> 38:06.701
I already said no to this, Ms. Wardwell.

38:06.784 --> 38:09.912
This is what your father
and mother wanted for you.

38:10.496 --> 38:13.040
That wasn't a lie your aunties told you.

38:13.332 --> 38:16.085
The circumstances, you must agree,
have changed.

38:16.877 --> 38:18.629
You're not the same girl,

38:18.713 --> 38:21.674
not the same witch you were
the night of the...

38:22.550 --> 38:24.302
ill-fated baptism.

38:24.802 --> 38:26.345
You have the potential

38:26.846 --> 38:29.807
to be the greatest witch
of your generation.

38:31.726 --> 38:33.894
There is a cost that comes with that.

38:33.978 --> 38:36.439
There has to be another way.

38:37.148 --> 38:38.816
There's not one I can think of.

38:40.818 --> 38:42.153
You must sign.

38:42.445 --> 38:45.573
It's the only way you'll ever
be strong enough to stop--

38:51.746 --> 38:53.039
That's him now.

38:54.915 --> 38:56.667
The Red Angel of Death.

38:57.668 --> 38:58.711
Can you hear him?

39:19.690 --> 39:21.233
I know you're scared, Sabrina.

39:21.734 --> 39:24.945
Because all women are taught
to fear power.

39:26.655 --> 39:28.657
Own your power.

39:29.408 --> 39:31.410
Don't accept it from the Dark Lord.

39:31.494 --> 39:33.371
Take it. Wield it.

39:34.288 --> 39:35.664
Save your friends.

39:35.748 --> 39:36.999
Ms. Wardwell...

39:37.333 --> 39:39.377
You've all but signed already.

39:39.460 --> 39:40.419
But...

39:41.462 --> 39:42.838
What's more important?

39:43.339 --> 39:48.636
That pissing contest with the Dark Lord,
or the salvation of your friends?

39:49.470 --> 39:51.931
If I sign...

39:52.640 --> 39:54.392
It is your destiny.

39:56.060 --> 39:59.271
If you do not, Harvey will die.

40:00.439 --> 40:02.525
Rosalind and Susie will die.

40:03.025 --> 40:05.945
Your aunts and your cousin will die.

40:06.028 --> 40:07.238
I will die.

40:07.696 --> 40:09.365
Please, Sabrina...

40:11.242 --> 40:12.910
for all our sakes.

40:18.916 --> 40:19.834
I'll sign.

40:31.554 --> 40:36.016
Do you do this of your own free will?

40:37.518 --> 40:42.606
And do you understand what it means?

40:44.316 --> 40:49.697
When I call on you, girl, you must answer.

41:15.306 --> 41:18.225
I shall deliver Sabrina unto you.

41:18.309 --> 41:19.727
Mom

41:19.810 --> 41:23.189
Oh, my child, you have
no idea how special you are, do you?

41:25.149 --> 41:27.067
There's no flying in my life...

41:28.360 --> 41:29.236
without you.

41:34.241 --> 41:36.452
You must sign the Book of the Beast!

41:36.535 --> 41:37.578
I can't do this.

41:37.661 --> 41:40.998
Sabrina Spellman
shall retain her mortal life,

41:41.081 --> 41:45.753
on the condition that she also attend
the Academy of Unseen Arts.

41:49.507 --> 41:52.009
-Are you ready to meet your fate?
-Prudence, please.

41:52.092 --> 41:54.595
I'm begging you, leave me alone.

41:54.678 --> 41:57.014
There's not a hope
in hell of that, half-breed.

41:57.473 --> 42:00.684
How am I ever going to outwit
the Dark Lord?

42:00.768 --> 42:03.270
Your parents died because of you.

42:07.733 --> 42:09.568
How's that feel?

42:10.402 --> 42:12.154
Not to have faith in anything?

42:15.366 --> 42:16.367
Mom, it's me.

42:16.992 --> 42:19.787
They took my baby after the baptism.

42:19.870 --> 42:22.081
They told me she had died.

42:23.249 --> 42:25.376
It's better to forget the mortal world.

42:26.168 --> 42:28.963
Harvey, please. Let me stay.
Let me at least help--

42:29.088 --> 42:30.297
No, Sabrina. You've...

42:30.381 --> 42:31.507
You've done enough.

42:34.510 --> 42:35.427
You have to go.

42:35.970 --> 42:39.390
Everything has a price.

42:40.516 --> 42:42.726
Edward learned that lesson.

42:43.185 --> 42:44.436
It's your turn now.

42:54.238 --> 42:56.740
Sabrina. Breathe. Let it in.

42:57.783 --> 43:00.494
-Can you feel it? Do you feel it.
-Yes.

43:01.787 --> 43:03.998
-We don't have much time.
-Where...

43:05.124 --> 43:06.125
Where do we go now?

43:07.459 --> 43:09.336
What do we do to stop the Thirteen...

43:09.795 --> 43:10.713
and the Red Angel?

43:12.506 --> 43:14.633
Not we, you.

43:15.551 --> 43:18.721
The power is yours, not ours.

