Where do I go?

43:21.890 --> 43:24.351
What do I do

43:25.936 --> 43:29.481
Hasn't the Dark Lord already shown you
what to do?

43:29.565 --> 43:30.566
What are you...?

43:31.483 --> 43:32.318
I don't...

43:43.120 --> 43:44.788
I was at the Hanging Tree.

43:49.335 --> 43:50.878
Where the witches died.

43:55.591 --> 43:57.259
It was on fire.

44:03.057 --> 44:06.477
We're nearly there, Lady Blackwood.
One more push.

44:07.645 --> 44:10.314
And here comes your first...

44:14.276 --> 44:15.569
What is it?

44:15.653 --> 44:18.447
Nothing. You're doing fine,
Lady Blackwood.

44:18.530 --> 44:20.574
Just think ofÂ how proud
the High Priest will be.

44:20.658 --> 44:22.201
Is he all right, my son?

44:22.284 --> 44:24.787
Strong and fine, Lady Blackwood.

44:24.870 --> 44:28.207
Sister Spellman,
Lady Blackwood's bleeding too much.

44:28.290 --> 44:29.708
We'll fix her right up.

44:30.292 --> 44:33.128
My babies... Sister Zelda, my babies.

44:33.629 --> 44:35.589
They must be preserved...

44:37.383 --> 44:38.801
...at all costs.

44:50.979 --> 44:52.356
Hilda, there you are.

44:52.439 --> 44:53.691
Dr. Cee?

44:54.650 --> 44:55.818
What are you doing?

44:55.901 --> 44:58.445
You should be downstairs.
I got so worried.

44:58.529 --> 45:02.282
I'm saying a little prayer
against the tornado.

45:02.366 --> 45:03.951
Do you need me to stay?

45:05.661 --> 45:09.081
Just hold my hands. Just for a minute.

45:10.916 --> 45:12.042
Will that help?

45:12.835 --> 45:14.128
It can't hurt, can it?

45:24.012 --> 45:27.141
Susie, what happened

45:27.224 --> 45:31.603
I have no clue.
Maybe she just got tired and went home?

45:32.187 --> 45:33.439
No, children.

45:34.314 --> 45:35.399
She left.

45:36.108 --> 45:37.568
She left...

45:38.902 --> 45:41.822
because it's his turn now.

45:41.905 --> 45:44.575
The Crimson Rider.

45:45.284 --> 45:47.453
The Angel of Death.

45:49.121 --> 45:50.539
Can't you hear him?

45:53.667 --> 45:55.335
That horse of his?

46:09.808 --> 46:12.728
-What the hell is that now?
-That, mortal, is the main event.

46:13.187 --> 46:14.563
The Doom of Greendale.

46:17.733 --> 46:19.526
You're not your father's
firstborn son, are you?

46:20.319 --> 46:21.945
No, that would have been Tommy.

46:22.446 --> 46:23.655
What about your father?

46:24.740 --> 46:26.950
He's the firstborn son, yeah.

46:35.542 --> 46:37.419
How do I do it, Ms. Wardwell?

46:38.295 --> 46:39.296
Dig deep.

46:39.379 --> 46:41.465
It isn't just power, Sabrina.

46:42.549 --> 46:43.842
It's rage.

46:44.927 --> 46:47.429
It's the desire to change the world...

46:48.263 --> 46:49.681
and the will to do it.

46:50.349 --> 46:52.559
Command the Greendale Thirteen.

46:58.357 --> 47:01.819
I order the Greendale Thirteen to stop!

47:04.112 --> 47:07.199
Go in peace, or face my wrath!

47:18.252 --> 47:20.462
Is that it

47:23.090 --> 47:25.342
No, it just got here.

47:26.260 --> 47:30.430
Tell me. You're not the firstborn
in your family, are you?

47:30.973 --> 47:32.558
Oldest of three boys.

47:34.768 --> 47:37.563
Hear me, hear me. Run away.
Live to see another day.

47:38.188 --> 47:41.191
Run! Go! I will be right behind you.

47:49.241 --> 47:52.077
Qui affecto protego,

47:52.160 --> 47:55.038
mixtisque iubas serpentibus.

47:57.833 --> 48:01.753
Qui affecto protego,
mixtisque iubas serpentibus

48:01.837 --> 48:04.339
et posteris meis stirpiqu.

48:05.465 --> 48:07.092
Qui affecto protego.

48:11.054 --> 48:13.098
Who are you to order us?

48:13.307 --> 48:16.268
We felt the wrath of Greendale once,
child.

48:16.643 --> 48:19.479
-We won't be hung again.
-No, not hung.

48:20.564 --> 48:21.732
Burned.

48:22.107 --> 48:23.901
Burn us, half-witch?

48:24.610 --> 48:26.236
We are not of this Earth.

48:26.320 --> 48:28.697
No earthly fire can burn us.

48:28.780 --> 48:30.699
No, not earthly fire.

48:31.742 --> 48:32.576
Hellfire.

48:32.659 --> 48:37.623
Devils.

48:37.831 --> 48:40.500
And in the history of witches,
only three--

48:40.584 --> 48:42.586
Well, it's about to be four.

48:42.961 --> 48:47.841
I, Sabrina Spellman,
daughter of Edward Spellman,

48:47.925 --> 48:53.472
Child of Night, call forth...
Fire from the Pit.

48:56.141 --> 48:59.102
Ater ignus, fusce fume.

48:59.561 --> 49:04.816
Te evoco ut potentium tuam monstres.

49:04.900 --> 49:08.070
Cupidibus flammis hic veni.

49:08.695 --> 49:12.616
Caelo sub isto, harc arborem consumo.

49:13.033 --> 49:16.578
Lucem tenebrasque tuas monstra.

49:16.912 --> 49:21.041
Impetuum tuum evoco ad devorandum.

49:21.416 --> 49:25.420
Hanc arborem ac omnes hospitas devora.

49:44.982 --> 49:47.609
And then they went up in hell flame.

49:47.693 --> 49:51.029
A gorgeous, searing inferno...

49:51.488 --> 49:53.448
consumed their souls.

49:55.325 --> 49:57.327
Releasing their anger...

49:59.121 --> 50:01.623
until their charred bodies

50:01.707 --> 50:04.167
fell from the sky...

50:05.544 --> 50:07.004
like ash.

50:17.889 --> 50:19.266
And once the witches

50:19.349 --> 50:21.309
who summoned
the Red Death were gone,

50:21.393 --> 50:24.604
and the wrath
that fueled him dissipated,

50:25.147 --> 50:26.481
the Angel, too...

50:27.649 --> 50:29.276
simply vanished

50:29.359 --> 50:31.153
as though he was never there.

50:32.029 --> 50:36.408
And just like that,
the witching hour was over.

50:36.783 --> 50:39.536
And most everyone had survived the storm,

50:39.953 --> 50:45.667
little knowing how close
to annihilation they'd come.

50:59.681 --> 51:00.849
What happened tonight?

51:01.224 --> 51:03.977
I'm pretty sure your girlfriend just saved
the entire town.

51:05.562 --> 51:06.813
She's not my girlfriend.

51:08.106 --> 51:09.024
Not anymore.

51:11.109 --> 51:12.611
Why did you show up here?

51:12.694 --> 51:14.488
She asked me, so I came.

51:16.448 --> 51:17.282
No, but...

51:18.325 --> 51:19.159
why?

51:20.702 --> 51:21.536
Are you...

51:22.412 --> 51:25.082
-Are you, guys--
-She loves you, mortal.

51:28.168 --> 51:29.336
She'd die for you.

51:30.462 --> 51:32.047
Maybe that's worth forgiving her.

51:41.306 --> 51:44.351
Faustus, I'm sorry, but you were right.

51:44.434 --> 51:47.729
Lady Blackwood was too weak
to bring your baby into the world.

51:47.813 --> 51:50.857
Baby? I thought you said twins.

51:53.401 --> 51:57.572
Something strange
but not unheard of happened.

51:58.657 --> 52:02.369
One of your sons, the dominant one...

52:03.620 --> 52:04.996
consumed the other,

52:05.080 --> 52:07.791
the submissive one, in the womb.

52:10.168 --> 52:12.003
There is only one son...

52:12.671 --> 52:15.048
fortified by the brother he consumed.

52:18.510 --> 52:19.636
As it should be.

52:21.221 --> 52:22.472
Let me hold him.

52:33.733 --> 52:35.610
My only begotten son...

52:40.740 --> 52:41.825
and heir!

53:44.262 --> 53:47.974
I don't know what you said in that prayer
tonight, but it certainly worked.

53:49.267 --> 53:50.727
All the clouds are cleared.

53:51.353 --> 53:53.772
It's going to be a beautiful day,
Hilda Spellman.

54:05.116 --> 54:05.992
Goodnight.

54:32.352 --> 54:35.146
What happened to you earlier?

54:36.731 --> 54:40.402
Doesn't matter.
All's well that ends well, I suppose.

54:40.485 --> 54:41.319
Hilda...

54:41.403 --> 54:42.320
Yes?

54:42.570 --> 54:45.490
I've done something rather impulsive.

54:54.207 --> 54:55.375
Did you make a magic baby?

54:55.458 --> 54:56.626
It's Lady Blackwood's.

54:56.918 --> 54:57.752
Hm?

54:57.836 --> 55:02.173
A girl. I lied to Father Blackwood.
I said he only had one child.

55:02.632 --> 55:03.550
Why?

55:04.259 --> 55:06.303
To protect the babe, Hilda.

55:07.470 --> 55:10.056
She's a girl, born before her brother.

55:10.932 --> 55:14.227
And the High Priest,
I feared what he would've done to her.

55:14.811 --> 55:17.480
But we can raise her.
We've done it before.

55:17.939 --> 55:21.651
We'll keep it a secret, you and I.
Together, as sisters.

55:21.735 --> 55:22.736
Forever and ever!

55:22.819 --> 55:24.070
I'm moving out.

55:24.195 --> 55:25.113
What?

55:25.697 --> 55:29.284
I'm moving out... of this bedroom.

55:29.659 --> 55:32.954
I think it's time I had a room of my own.

55:45.425 --> 55:47.510
The Church of Night is ours, boys.

55:48.511 --> 55:50.388
This is the Dark Lord's sign.

55:51.473 --> 55:52.515
His blessing...

55:53.308 --> 55:55.018
that we are in the right.

55:56.603 --> 56:00.023
Hail to my firstborn son.

56:00.815 --> 56:02.025
Hail Judas!

56:02.150 --> 56:04.569
Hail Judas! Hail Satan!

56:04.652 --> 56:06.988
Hail Judas! Hail Satan!

56:07.072 --> 56:09.366
Hail Judas! Hail Satan!

56:09.449 --> 56:10.283
Hail Judas!

56:25.423 --> 56:27.634
You... changed your hair.

56:28.510 --> 56:29.594
Yeah.

56:30.720 --> 56:32.222
Thanks for sending that guy, Nick.

56:33.473 --> 56:34.391
He...

56:36.142 --> 56:37.852
He said you saved the whole town tonight.

56:39.145 --> 56:41.648
Well, it was a group effort.

56:44.651 --> 56:46.236
I wanted to check on you.

56:47.404 --> 56:50.281
And apologize again, Harvey.

56:51.366 --> 56:53.993
For all the secrets, for Tommy.

56:55.078 --> 56:56.079
For everything.

56:57.789 --> 57:00.208
I truly am sorry.

57:00.291 --> 57:01.292
I know.

57:03.795 --> 57:04.838
I know you are.

57:05.338 --> 57:06.881
So, what if you we start over?

57:09.259 --> 57:10.802
No more secrets this time. We just--

57:10.885 --> 57:11.803
I don't...

57:13.930 --> 57:15.807
I don't think that's such a good idea.

57:17.725 --> 57:19.185
I don't know if it's safe...

57:20.145 --> 57:21.479
for me to be around you.

57:22.313 --> 57:23.148
Or Roz...

57:24.232 --> 57:25.316
or Susie.

57:25.400 --> 57:26.276
Why not?

57:27.152 --> 57:29.028
I had to do something tonight...

57:31.197 --> 57:32.323
that scares me.

57:33.032 --> 57:33.867
Harvey...

57:36.619 --> 57:38.163
it touched something...

57:39.747 --> 57:42.167
dark inside me.

57:44.878 --> 57:48.465
I love you too much to risk
anything bad happening to you.

57:57.432 --> 57:58.266
Can I...

58:00.560 --> 58:02.145
Can I get one last kiss?

58:23.166 --> 58:25.084
And that, as they say...

58:25.835 --> 58:26.669
was that.

58:27.253 --> 58:29.506
All things according to his plan.

58:30.548 --> 58:33.384
Though I never really get
the credit I deserve.

58:34.719 --> 58:37.138
The best and worst things...

58:38.139 --> 58:39.390
happen in the shadows.

58:40.808 --> 58:45.438
Well, this is all a very long-winded way
of my telling you that...

58:47.190 --> 58:50.026
I'm an amazing teacher,
Principal Hawthorne.

58:51.444 --> 58:55.865
No one but me could've gotten Sabrina
so far along the Path of Night.

58:57.534 --> 58:59.452
Who the hell are you, lady?

59:02.038 --> 59:03.039
Who am I?

59:06.209 --> 59:08.086
Well, I'm not Mary Wardwell...

59:08.795 --> 59:10.505
though I do enjoy her body.

59:12.840 --> 59:16.719
I'm the Mother of Demons,
the Dawn of Doom,

59:17.470 --> 59:19.138
Satan's concubine.

59:20.640 --> 59:22.350
I'm Lilith, dear boy.

59:23.268 --> 59:24.686
First wife to Adam,

59:24.811 --> 59:27.897
saved from despair by a fallen angel.

59:28.731 --> 59:33.278
I call myself Madame Satan in his honor.

59:35.071 --> 59:36.155
But soon...

59:37.907 --> 59:38.783
very soon...

59:40.868 --> 59:42.537
I'll have a new title.

59:43.246 --> 59:44.163
You see...

59:47.125 --> 59:51.796
once I finish grooming Sabrina
to take my place as Satan's foot-soldier,

59:54.132 --> 59:58.094
I'll earn a crown
and a throne by his side.

1:00:02.640 --> 1:00:03.975
Who am I?

1:00:15.278 --> 1:00:17.655
I'm the future Queen of Hell.

1:00:26.039 --> 1:00:27.957
I did so leave you leftovers.

1:00:29.959 --> 1:00:32.086
Oh, stop squawking, and just say it.

1:00:32.754 --> 1:00:33.963
Forgive me, madame,

1:00:34.047 --> 1:00:36.174
but doesn't it seem
that Satan is grooming Sabrina

1:00:36.257 --> 1:00:38.468
to reign at his side, not you?

1:00:40.053 --> 1:00:44.974
But the Dark Lord wouldn't betray
my eternal service like that, Stolas.

1:00:46.726 --> 1:00:48.061
Even if he would,

1:00:49.103 --> 1:00:53.024
there would be a very simple way
to deal with Sabrina.

1:01:08.539 --> 1:01:10.875
She's still Sabrina, Harvey.

1:01:11.209 --> 1:01:12.835
She's still the girl we know.

1:01:13.044 --> 1:01:14.462
I don't know, Susie.

1:01:14.545 --> 1:01:16.005
Something had changed,

1:01:16.547 --> 1:01:17.715
and not just her hair.

1:01:18.800 --> 1:01:21.928
But she's still coming to school, right?

1:01:24.013 --> 1:01:25.848
I mean, we're still her friends?
